<div class="dw-pane" id="pane-m6">
  <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#22c55e;margin-bottom:4px">&#128247; Visual Brand Protection</div>
  <div style="font-size:12px;color:#64748b;margin-bottom:16px">crt.sh CT logs + typosquat detection + visual similarity scoring + auto-takedown</div>
